Your adventure begins in an unusual city where you can find many useful and unique items to interact with. You will meet a police officer and a seller of alien devices, and during the game you will get acquainted with unusual creatures. Each item and character creates a huge fascinating story.

You need to get into the neighbor’s house. You will find many traps, obstacles, locks and closed doors. If you are careful, you will outsmart all opponents, solve the puzzles, get to the mysterious basement and find out what the neighbor is hiding.

This is a free game, but some items and abilities can also be bought for real money. It can make it easier for you to complete and add new fascinating experiences.

If you have any questions or suggestions for the game, please contact our support at support@pagagroup.com.ua
